01:15:48,200 --> 01:15:49,233
Tia: CARRIE?

942
01:15:55,133 --> 01:15:56,666
- CARRIE?
- TIA.

943
01:16:03,100 --> 01:16:07,466
- [ bangs on door ]
- [ gasps ]

944
01:16:07,466 --> 01:16:10,900
"OUR FATHER,
WHO ART IN HEAVEN

945
01:16:10,900 --> 01:16:12,233
HALLOWED BY THY NAME.

946
01:16:12,233 --> 01:16:13,866
THY KINGDOM COME,
THY WILL BE DONE

947
01:16:13,866 --> 01:16:15,466
ON EARTH
AS IT IS IN HEAVEN.

948
01:16:15,466 --> 01:16:17,133
GIVE US THIS DAY
OUR DAILY BREAD

949
01:16:17,133 --> 01:16:18,966
AND FORGIVE US--

950
01:16:18,966 --> 01:16:19,733
[ banging on door ]

951
01:16:24,633 --> 01:16:25,766
[ banging stops ]

952
01:16:34,700 --> 01:16:36,066
[ whispers ]
"HAIL MARY FULL OF GRACE

953
01:16:36,066 --> 01:16:37,500
THE LORD IS WITH THEE.

954
01:16:37,500 --> 01:16:39,600
BLESSED ART THOU AMONGST WOMEN,

955
01:16:39,600 --> 01:16:41,333
AND BLESSED IS THE FRUIT
OF THY WOMB, JESUS."

956
01:16:41,333 --> 01:16:42,733
[ rattling ]

957
01:16:51,100 --> 01:16:52,166
[ screams ]

958
01:16:59,000 --> 01:17:01,200
"OUR FATHER WHO ART IN HEAVEN
HALLOWED BY THY NAME

959
01:17:01,200 --> 01:17:03,133
THY KINGDOM COME
THY WILL BE DONE

960
01:17:03,133 --> 01:17:06,100
ON EARTH
AS IT IS IN HEAVEN.

961
01:17:06,100 --> 01:17:07,633
GIVE US THIS DAY
OUR DAILY BREAD

962
01:17:07,633 --> 01:17:09,366
AND FORGIVE US
OUR TRESPASSES

963
01:17:09,366 --> 01:17:11,733
AS WE FORGIVE THOSE
WHO TRESPASS AGAINST US.

964
01:17:11,733 --> 01:17:13,100
[ screams ]

965
01:18:49,633 --> 01:18:51,433
[ door opens ]

966
01:18:51,433 --> 01:18:52,366
MOM?

967
01:18:58,133 --> 01:18:59,900
WHAT THE HELL?

968
01:18:59,900 --> 01:19:02,166
CARRIE?

969
01:19:02,166 --> 01:19:03,666
CARRIE!

970
01:19:03,666 --> 01:19:06,266
MOM, MOM, MOM!

971
01:19:06,266 --> 01:19:07,133
OH, MY GOD!
WHAT HAS HAPPENED HERE?

972
01:19:07,133 --> 01:19:09,333
WHERE'S TIA?

973
01:19:09,333 --> 01:19:10,666
THERE WAS ALL THESE THINGS
AT THE DOOR--

974
01:19:10,666 --> 01:19:12,366
HONEY, YOU'RE BLEEDING!

975
01:19:12,366 --> 01:19:13,566
- THE BATHROOM--
- [ knocks on door ]

976
01:19:18,833 --> 01:19:19,766
HI.

977
01:19:25,433 --> 01:19:28,966
SAMANTHA MAY WE...
SPEAK TO YOU IN PRIVATE?

978
01:19:28,966 --> 01:19:30,133
SURE.

979
01:19:35,900 --> 01:19:37,266
Sam: [ clears throat ]

980
01:19:37,266 --> 01:19:39,500
IS EVERYTHING OKAY?

981
01:19:39,500 --> 01:19:40,766
SAMANTHA,
THIS IS OFFICER HARDY.

982
01:19:40,766 --> 01:19:41,600
HI.

983
01:19:45,366 --> 01:19:49,700
I THOUGHT I SHOULD BE
THE ONE TO TELL YOU

984
01:19:49,700 --> 01:19:54,566
I'M SORRY SAMANTHA,
TIA'S DEAD.

985
01:19:54,566 --> 01:19:57,266
Heather:
IS EVERYTHING OKAY?

986
01:19:57,266 --> 01:19:58,566
HANG ON A SECOND, HONEY.

987
01:19:58,566 --> 01:20:00,966
EXCUSE ME?

988
01:20:00,966 --> 01:20:03,466
IS THIS SOME KIND OF JOKE?

989
01:20:03,466 --> 01:20:06,166
I MEAN, I'M REALLY
NOT FINDING THIS FUNNY, SO...

990
01:20:06,166 --> 01:20:08,266
I'M AFRAID IT'S NOT,
SAMANTHA.

991
01:20:08,266 --> 01:20:10,000
IT SEEMS SHE WAS PLAYING
YESTERDAY

992
01:20:10,000 --> 01:20:12,233
AFTER SCHOOL BEHIND
THE SCHOOLHOUSE,

993
01:20:12,233 --> 01:20:14,666
BY THE AIR CONDITIONING UNIT.

994
01:20:14,666 --> 01:20:18,133
SHE WAS ALL BY HERSELF.
THERE WAS NO ONE THERE.

995
01:20:18,133 --> 01:20:20,200
- THE STAIRS ARE SO STEEP--
- NO.

996
01:20:20,200 --> 01:20:21,633
SHE MUST HAVE FALLEN
AND HIT HER HEAD.

997
01:20:21,633 --> 01:20:23,900
SHE HASN'T EVEN BEEN
TO SCHOOL TODAY, SO--

998
01:20:23,900 --> 01:20:26,633
THERE WAS NO ONE THERE
TO HELP HER, SAMANTHA.

999
01:20:26,633 --> 01:20:29,033
SHE HIT HER HEAD.

1000
01:20:29,033 --> 01:20:30,800
Hardy: MRS. LEE,
YOUR DAUGHTER'S BODY

1001
01:20:30,800 --> 01:20:32,600
WAS DISCOVERED THIS MORNING

1002
01:20:32,600 --> 01:20:35,366
THE CORONER'S ESTIMATED
THE TIME OF DEATH

1003
01:20:35,366 --> 01:20:37,100
AT 4:00 P.M.
YESTERDAY AFTERNOON.

1004
01:20:47,133 --> 01:20:48,500
MOMMY!

1005
01:20:48,500 --> 01:20:49,900
JESUS!

1006
01:20:49,900 --> 01:20:53,033
ALL RIGHT, PAUSE.

1007
01:20:53,033 --> 01:20:56,133
YOU BROUGHT MY DAUGHTER HOME
YESTERDAY AFTERNOON, REMEMBER?

1008
01:20:56,133 --> 01:20:57,666
I WISH THE HELL THAT I HAD,
SAMANTHA.

1009
01:20:57,666 --> 01:20:59,533
I WISHED I HAD.

1010
01:20:59,533 --> 01:20:59,766
SHE'D BE ALIVE TODAY,
BUT I DIDN'T.

1011
01:21:03,766 --> 01:21:07,766
HONEY, I'M SO SORRY.

1012
01:21:07,766 --> 01:21:10,000
- HELLO.
- HI.

1013
01:21:10,000 --> 01:21:11,800
CLEARLY,
YOU WERE TO UNDERSTAND

1014
01:21:11,800 --> 01:21:13,700
- I'M NOT ALLOWED TO BRING...
- OFFICER...

1015
01:21:13,700 --> 01:21:14,833
- A CHILD HOME FROM SCHOOL.
- THIS MAN IS LYING.

1016
01:21:14,833 --> 01:21:17,033
THAT IS AN ABSOLUTE LIE!

1017
01:21:17,033 --> 01:21:20,066
I DIDN'T BRING YOUR DAUGHTER
HOME YESTERDAY, SAMANTHA.

1018
01:21:20,066 --> 01:21:21,400
PLEASE DON'T TURN
THE LIGHTS OFF.

1019
01:21:24,633 --> 01:21:26,433
Aaron: EVERY
ONCE IN A WHILE,

1020
01:21:26,433 --> 01:21:27,833
THE SPIRIT DOESN'T KNOW
THAT HE IS DEAD.

1021
01:21:27,833 --> 01:21:29,633
HE IS TRAPPED
IN A CERTAIN LOCATION.

1022
01:21:29,633 --> 01:21:31,600
I THINK THIS HOUSE
IS HAUNTED.

1023
01:21:31,600 --> 01:21:33,200
AN EXORCISM?

1024
01:21:33,200 --> 01:21:34,200
IF THERE'S SOMETHING
IN THE HOUSE,

1025
01:21:34,200 --> 01:21:35,233
WE'LL GET IT OUT.

1026
01:21:35,233 --> 01:21:39,666
WHY DO YOU HATE ME?

1027
01:21:39,666 --> 01:21:41,566
Aaron: SOME SPIRITS
WILL REFUSE TO LEAVE

1028
01:21:41,566 --> 01:21:44,633
EVEN AFTER THEY LEARN
OF THEIR OWN DEATH.

1029
01:21:44,633 --> 01:21:45,333
I'LL NEVER LEAVE.

1030
01:21:48,800 --> 01:21:52,300
WE DRIVE FROM US,
WHOEVER YOU MAY BE!

1031
01:21:52,300 --> 01:21:56,400
YOU DON'T WANT ME HERE.

1032
01:21:56,400 --> 01:21:58,166
Aaron: THIS NEGATIVE EMOTION
CAN FESTER

1033
01:21:58,166 --> 01:21:59,733
STRIPPING THE SPIRIT
OF ANY HUMANITY

1034
01:21:59,733 --> 01:22:00,566
LEAVING ONLY
AN ANGRY ENTITY.

1035
01:22:05,633 --> 01:22:08,900
"OUR FATHER, WHO ART IN
HEAVEN HALLOWED BY THY NAME

1036
01:22:08,900 --> 01:22:11,000
THY KINGDOM COME,
THY WILL BE DONE

1037
01:22:11,000 --> 01:22:12,700
ON EARTH
AS IT IS IN HEAVEN."

1038
01:22:12,700 --> 01:22:14,233
[ screams ]

1039
01:22:18,500 --> 01:22:21,133
CLEARLY, I-- I TOLD YOU
YESTERDAY

1040
01:22:21,133 --> 01:22:23,500
THAT LEGALLY,
I'M NOT ALLOWED--

1041
01:22:23,500 --> 01:22:24,966
- LEGALLY!
- TO BRING A CHILD HOME
FROM SCHOOL.

1042
01:22:24,966 --> 01:22:25,933
OFFICER, COULD YOU PLEASE
HAVE THIS MAN REMOVED

1043
01:22:25,933 --> 01:22:27,066
FROM MY PROPERTY?

1044
01:22:27,066 --> 01:22:28,833
I DON'T KNOW WHO YOU ARE.

1045
01:22:28,833 --> 01:22:30,100
I REALLY DON'T KNOW
WHAT YOUR PROBLEM IS.

1046
01:22:30,100 --> 01:22:32,600
BUT I-- JUST GET--
ABSOLUTELY--

1047
01:22:32,600 --> 01:22:36,466
MRS. LEE!
I'M VERY SORRY
FOR YOUR LOSS.

1048
01:22:36,466 --> 01:22:37,866
YOU'LL HAVE TO ACCOMPANY ME
TO THE MORGUE

1049
01:22:37,866 --> 01:22:40,833
TO IDENTIFY THE BODY
OF YOUR DAUGHTER.

1050
01:22:40,833 --> 01:22:41,766
Lew: I'M SORRY, SAMANTHA.

1051
01:22:56,966 --> 01:22:57,700
[ gasps ]

1052
01:23:00,566 --> 01:23:02,033
TIA?

1053
01:23:06,600 --> 01:23:07,500
TIA?

1054
01:23:10,133 --> 01:23:12,500
HONEY?

1055
01:23:12,500 --> 01:23:15,000
TIA?

1056
01:23:15,000 --> 01:23:16,700
OH, MY POOR BABY.

1057
01:23:16,700 --> 01:23:17,900
TIA!

1058
01:23:17,900 --> 01:23:19,100
MY BABY...

1059
01:23:19,100 --> 01:23:22,733
OH, NO!

1060
01:23:22,733 --> 01:23:25,166
OH, TIA,
I'M SO SORRY.

1061
01:23:25,166 --> 01:23:26,166
[ deep voice ] MOMMY!

1062
01:23:26,166 --> 01:23:26,700
[ screaming ]

